name: wagon trail, interesting tales
description:
wagons of the past, wagons of the present, my smokeshack i'm hotboxing now... we're all the same, right?

-

november 9th, 2021

i wanna be well spoken
DixieLand raised, twang
at end of voice.
i want the perceptions of 
myself from others to 
be well based, not just in
first impressions cause
come on dude, how is a 
biblically accurate ball of anxiety
like me gonna have
room to breathe?
